L&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAoZbVkvcjl9DvVmU9_UjcybSVMTH8T-JM5RqDd1t6eng&oe=670E61B7"}, {"file_name": "vlcsnap-00008.png", "id": "7282727451839924", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035307_7282727458506590_4830324704851622877_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=oNwK3qIRjXQQ7kNvgFu8-Gm&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAGjoIQMdCwHQoFpPAWj6U4-0Rtzoxh9cULJESL2_qqrw&oe=670E5E2E"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "landscapefull3.png", "id": "1181005139718728", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036670_1181005143052061_709758329527305958_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=K38Fb0L5imUQ7kNvgHxbT6e&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD72kgZCsiCW3kdziUdc0jIb8lMiTbkvIDmyaBSA3x-ww&oe=670E58F2"}, "display_name": "3D Mahjong worlds - Quest", "keywords": ["strategy", "mahjong", "board", "relax", "classic"], "long_description": "This is the VR implementation of the classic Mahjong game\n\nWhether you are a mahjong master or a beginner, this game will be your best choice!\nCreative design of solid 3D mahjong levels, and simple game rules, suitable for everyone!\nIt\u2019s transformed from the traditional matching game and brings a relaxing experience to players in a 3D way.\nBe the master and pair all the cubes to eliminate them on over 30 levels!\n\nGame features:\n\n- 30 levels\n- Classic and 3D style levels.\n- Rotate, move and zoom the board.\n- English, Hungarian and Simplified Chinese languages.\n- Relaxing environment.\n", "short_description": "This is the VR implementation of the classic Mahjong game\n\nNo matter if you are a mahjong master or a beginner, this game will be your best choice!\nCreative design of solid 3D mahjong levels, and simple game rules!"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "logo2-chinese.png", "id": "1628457724592817", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscd